metadata.description: These are nice plugins for mixing ;)

reapack.name: NC76 (Tukan)
reapack.desc: NC76 (Tukan) - A FET style 76ish Compressor with punch, sidechain and trick

reapack.name: Delaymachine (Tukan)
reapack.desc: Delaymachine (Tukan) - A delay with pingpong mode and tape delay mode

reapack.name: Exciter+Sub (Tukan)
reapack.desc: Exciter+Sub (Tukan) - Type C copy – Exciter and Subbass

reapack.name: ExpGate 2 (Tukan)
reapack.desc: ExpGate 2 (Tukan) - Gate and expander with invert mode and sidechain

reapack.name: LA-1A (Tukan)
reapack.desc: LA-1A (Tukan) - Famous optical Compressor with tube output stage

reapack.name: Tukan reverb bundle (Tukan)
reapack.desc: Three different reverb plugins: Spring with tremolo, 80s FDL, PCM algorithmic Reverb

reapack.name: PreAmp (Tukan)
reapack.desc: PreAmp (Tukan) - A preamp that can also drive distortion, shelving Eqs

reapack.name: Tape (Tukan)
reapack.desc: Tape (Tukan) - A tape machine – can also lofi your sounds if needed

reapack.name: Compressor 2 (Tukan)
reapack.desc: Compressor 2 (Tukan) - A clean compressor, featuring sidechain and trick
